## Local Development (Flask + Git)

1. Set your secret authentication token:
   ```bash
   export TINYHUB_TOKEN="your_secure_auth_token"
   ```
2. Run the application:
   ```bash
   pip install flask
   python app.py
   ```
3. Open `http://127.0.0.1:5000` to view the uploader.

