## GET Uploader Workaround

To write code via a GET request (bypassing AI POST tool barriers), the AI must generate an HMAC-SHA256 signature of `${proj}:${filepath}:${message}` using your `signing_secret` config key and request the following format:

```
GET https://<your-project-id>.web.app/api/commit-get/my-app?sig=<hex_signature>&f=src/main.js&m=Update+Message&c=<base64_data>
```
